dcterms:creator: A. L. Traud
P. J. Mucha
M. A. Porter
dcterms:description: The Facebook100 dataset includes a complete set of people from Facebook networks for 100 different colleges and universities in the USA, recorded at a single moment of time in September 2005. It contains information about friendships and limited demographic information such as student/faculty status, gender, major, dormitory, year, and high school.
dcterms:title: Facebook100

dcterms:creator: A. L. Traud
E. D. Kelsic
P. J. Mucha
M. A. Porter
dcterms:description: This dataset is a variant of the Facebook100 dataset specifically used for the analysis of link prediction, focusing on the performance and evaluation of multiple machine learning algorithms on different feature sets derived from the Facebook100 network.
dcterms:title: Facebook100 (for the analysis of link prediction)

dcterms:creator: R. A. Rossi

dcterms:description: The Network Data Repository provides a collection of network datasets along with interactive graph analytics and visualization tools, facilitating research in network science.
dcterms:title: Network Data Repository
